{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 73,
  "title": "第七十三章（天網）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "勇於敢者則殺 勇於不敢者則栝 此兩者或利或害"
    },
    {
      "text": "天之所惡 孰知亓故"
    },
    {
      "text": "天之道 不彈而善勝 不言而善應 不召而自來 彈而善謀"
    },
    {
      "text": "天網恢恢 疏而不失"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "勇敢有為，則殺其身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "勇於不敢有為，則活其身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂敢與不敢也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 18,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "活身為利，殺身為害。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "惡有為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "誰能知天意之故而不犯？",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言聖人之明德猶難於勇敢，況無聖人之德而欲行之乎？",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天不與人爭貴賤，而人自畏之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天不言，萬物自動以應時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天不呼召，萬物皆負陰而向陽。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "繟，寬也。天道雖寬博，善謀慮人事，修善行惡，各蒙其報也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天所網羅恢恢甚大，雖疏遠，司察人善惡，無有所失。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "必不得其死也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "必齊命也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 15,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "俱勇而所施者異，利害不同，故曰，或利或害也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。言誰能知天下之所惡意故邪？其唯聖人。夫聖人之明，猶難於勇敢，況無聖人之明而欲行之也。故曰，猶難之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天唯不爭，故天下莫能與之爭。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "順則吉，逆則凶，不言而善應也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "處下則物自歸。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "垂象而見吉凶，先事而設誠，安而不忘危，未召而謀之，故曰，繟然而善謀也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
